lead_paragraph: Stefan Elliott scored on a point shot through traffic 1:47 into the third period and the Arizona Coyotes beat the Calgary Flames 2-1 on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Elliott Scores Early in 3rd to Lift Coyotes Over Flames 2-1
